high_descs: Turn and go to the beige tvstand under the tv.
Pick up the ladle on the TV stand.
Turn right and then take a left into the bathroom and go to the sink.
Put the ladle in the sink and rinse it off and pick it up.
Leave the bathroom take a right and go into the sidetable straight ahead on your right.
Put the ladle on the sidetable.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a ladle off and put it on the side table.

high_descs: Turn right and head straight, then hang left towards the sofa.
Pick up spatula from the sofa.
Go straight towards the wall and then walk straight into the room, turning to the sink on your right.
wash spatula on the sink then take it back.
Turn around and head straight, then proceed to turn left towards the side table.
Place spatula on the side table.
anns.task_desc: washing spatula on the sink and placing it clean.

high_descs: Take the Cooking utensil in the tv stand
Put the Cooking utensil in the sink, clean it off
Take back in the Cooking utensil
Place the Cooking utensil on the side table
anns.task_desc: Take the Cooking utensil in the tv stand clean the Cooking utensil place the Cooking utensil on the side table
